@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.83
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.90 * v1 + 0.02)) - wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.82)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.75) - tmp)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.62 / v0 + 0.57) + 0.74) / (v0 + (v2 + 0.62 - tmp + 0.03)))
    v0 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = (v0 + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
